  <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/bunkyboy/image/upload/v1654206591/Walking_around-cuate_bckdoz.png" alt="lonely" align="left"><br><br>
    <h3>How It Works</h3><br>
      <p>As a helper or a commuter: 1. connect to people nearby. 2. store family and friends in an easy access contact list. 3. quick links to pre-programmed emergency numbers. </p>
</div>

<div class="more-info">
  <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/bunkyboy/image/upload/v1654206602/3936748_h0ebk1.jpg" alt="lonely" align="right"><br><br>
